# Client Architecture

The client runs in the browser and performs:

* rendering
* player input
* scene updates
* server communication

```
Client

 ├ Rendering Engine
 │   └ Three.js
 │
 ├ Game Systems
 │   ├ Player Controller
 │   ├ World Logic
 │   ├ Physics
 │
 ├ Networking
 │   ├ WebSocket Client
 │   └ State Sync
 │
 └ UI Layer
     └ HUD / Chat / Menus
```

